title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight -  Dassault Dornier Carreidas 160
description:
In this video we will look at version 0.51 of the Dassault Dornier Carreidas 160. The Dassault Dornier Carreidas 160 is another fighter which you can add to your flight simulator install. Keep in mind the aircraft is still under development and some of the functionalities are not working yet as expected. 

If you also want to give the aircraft a try you can download it from the site below:
https://flightsim.to/file/7236/dassault-dornier-alpha-jet-dev-version-0-25
